<h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
<h3 id="rows">Sensible row size</h3>
<p>The default is three rows, i.e. three lines of text, but you should set a number that makes the most sense for your use case. For example, a chat app makes sense to take the default of three, but a customer feedback form should likely have 5-10. Note that text areas are resizable so the user can extend it further if needed, just take care to set a sensible default.</p>
<h3 id="a11y">Accessibility</h3>
<p>There are no accessibility recommendations for text area.</p>
